<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>One-Time Password (OTP)</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #365CCE;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .token {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background-color: #F3F4F6;
            color: #365CCE;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .note {
            color: #555555;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>One-Time Password (OTP)</h1>
        <p>Dear {{email}},</p>
        <p>Your secure One-Time Password (OTP) is:</p>
        <div class="token">{{token}}</div>
        <p>This OTP is valid for a limited time to enhance your account security. If you did not request this OTP, please contact us immediately.</p>
        <p class="note">Please do not share this OTP with anyone for your security.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; {{currentYear}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
